              Regelm√§√üige Treffen mit Gaming-Stationen, kreativen Ecken und Raum zum Ankommen,
              Ausprobieren und neue Leute kennenlernen.
            </p>
          </article>

          <article class="event-highlight-card">
            <h3>üß† Workshops &amp; Sessions</h3>
            <p>
              Von IT-Grundlagen √ºber Medienkompetenz bis zu KI &amp; digitalen Tools ‚Äì praxisnah,
              alltagsrelevant und gemeinsam mit der Community gestaltet.
            </p>
          </article>

          <article class="event-highlight-card">
            <h3>ü§ù Projekte &amp; Kooperationen</h3>
            <p>
              Spezielle Formate mit Schulen, Jugendzentren, Vereinen und Partnern ‚Äì mit Fokus auf
              Teilhabe, Empowerment und moderner Jugendkultur.
            </p>
          </article>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .page-events {
    padding-bottom: 4rem;
  }

  .events-hero {
    padding-top: 3.5rem;
    padding-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .eyebrow {
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.22em;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    margin-bottom: 0.6rem;
  }

  .events-title {
    font-size: clamp(2.1rem, 3vw, 2.7rem);
    line-height: 1.1;
    font-weight: 800;
    color: var(--text-main);
    margin-bottom: 0.7rem;
  }

  .events-lead {
    font-size: 1.02rem;
    max-width: 40rem;
    color: var(--text-main);
    margin-bottom: 1.3rem;
  }

  .events-tags {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 0.5rem;
  }

  .events-tags span {
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    padding: 0.35rem 0.75rem;
    border-radius: 999px;
    border: 1px solid var(--border-soft);
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);
  }

  .calendar-card {
    padding: 1.8rem 1.6rem 1.6rem;
    border-radius: 1.5rem;
    background: #ffffff;
    border: 1px solid var(--border-soft);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-soft);
  }

  .calendar-header h2 {
    font-size: 1.4rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.4rem;
  }

  .calendar-header p {
    font-size: 0.96rem;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    max-width: 36rem;
  }

  .calendar-embed {
    margin-top: 1.4rem;
    border-radius: 1.2rem;
    overflow: hidden;
    border: 1px solid var(--border-soft);
    background: var(--bg-soft);
  }

  .calendar-embed iframe {
    display: block;
    width: 100%;
    height: 600px;
    border: 0;
  }

  .calendar-hint {
    margin-top: 0.9rem;
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    color: var(--text-muted);
  }

  .section-soft {
    background: radial-gradient(circle at top left, rgba(148, 163, 255, 0.08), transparent 55%);
  }

  .events-grid {
    display: grid;
    gap: 1.4rem;
    margin-top: 1.4rem;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(240px, 1fr));
  }

  .event-highlight-card {
    padding: 1.4rem 1.3rem;
    border-radius: 1.3rem;
    background: #ffffff;
    border: 1px solid var(--border-soft);
    box-shadow: 0 10px 28px rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.06);
  }

  .event-highlight-card h3 {
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.4rem;
  }

  .event-highlight-card p {
    font-size: 0.94rem;
    color: var(--text-main);
  }

  @media (max-width: 720px) {
    .events-hero {
      padding-top: 3rem;
    }

    .calendar-card {
      padding: 1.5rem 1.3rem 1.4rem;
    }

    .calendar-embed iframe {
      height: 480px;
    }
  }
</style>
